column2: Baldur's Gate 2 Enhanced Edition: Shadows of Amn — Introduction
column7:
Welcome to Baldur's Gate 2 Enhanced Edition: Shadows of Amn! This playthrough utilizes the version of Elmindreda that I created (using the same stats) for my stream-exclusive playthrough of the Enhanced Edition of Baldur's Gate, with the intention of importing her into Siege of Dragonspear and Baldur's Gate 2. Join me for yet another of the Avatar's adventures!

---------------------------------------------
